Package: rvatk
Title: Rare Variant Analysis Toolkit
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Matt Halvorsen [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Matt Halvorsen <mhalvors1@gmail.com>
Authors@R: person("Matt", "Halvorsen", email = "mhalvors1@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Package that allows for easier analysis of rare variant genetic data.
             Includes libraries for interfacing with filetypes used at the Institute of Genomic 
             Medicine at Columbia University, as well as other common file types such as plink BED.
             Also includes scripts that utilize the package for rare variant analysis.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.2)
License: GPL (>= 2)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Suggests:
    testthat
Imports:
    snpStats,
    data.table,
    methods
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
